    <abstract>
      <t>Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (BFD) mechanisms can be used for
   fast detection of failures in the forwarding path of SR Policy. This
   document describes the encapsulation of BFD for SRv6 Policy. The BFD
   packets may be encapsulated in Insert-mode or Encaps-mode.</t>
    </abstract>
